Today, we found all our weights
[INAUDIBLE] one every mile.

00:01:14.230 --> 00:01:16.090
Everyone grabbed an extra one.

00:01:16.090 --> 00:01:19.560
By the end, we all had a weight, and we
all carried the fallen through the end.

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:21.970
The ribbons that we
carry today were actually

00:01:21.970 --> 00:01:26.050
of men who've been killed
in action, and also those

